    <title>VPS使用mono+ASF云挂卡</title>
    <link href="https://huangjiaming.com/2017/05/12/vps2/"/>
    <id>https://huangjiaming.com/2017/05/12/vps2/</id>
    <published>2017-05-12T11:02:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-06-02T09:49:33.845Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<script src="/assets/js/DPlayer.min.js"> </script><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js"> </script><p>继上篇文章介绍了VPS安装shadowsocks翻墙后，我们就有了一台VPS，但VPS显然不能只用来翻墙，本篇教程介绍的是使用mono运行ASF在VPS上云挂卡</p>
<p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/18/591d51c733499.jpeg" alt=""></p>
<iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="330" height="450" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=0&id=157137810&auto=1&height=430"></iframe>

<hr>
<ol>
<li><p>如果你不是steamer<br>欢迎入坑<del>记得加我</del><br><a href="http://store.steampowered.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">Steam</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Steam是美国电子游戏商威尔乌于2003年9月12日推出的数位发行、数字版权管理及社交系统，它用于数位软体及游戏的发行销售与后续更新，支援Windows、OS X和Linux等作业系统，是目前全球最大的PC电子游戏平台。</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><p>steam集换式卡牌<br>详见<a href="https://steamcommunity.com/tradingcards/faq/Steam?l=schinese" target="_blank" rel="external">steam集换式卡牌</a></p>
</li>
<li><p>本地ASF挂卡<br>详见<br>（入门）<a href="https://steamcn.com/t187323-1-1" target="_blank" rel="external">ASF图形配置程序设置</a><br>（高级）<a href="https://steamcn.com/t176404-1-1" target="_blank" rel="external">ArchiSteamFarm(ASF)掛卡配置與命令教程</a><br>（自定义）<a href="https://steamcn.com/t187703-1-1" target="_blank" rel="external">ASF官方维基中文版</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p>提示：steamcn是非官方站点</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<p>附上我自己的ASF配置文件，仅供参考 huangjiamianbao.json<br><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"AcceptGifts"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"CardDropsRestricted"</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"CustomGamePlayedWhileFarming"</span>: <span class="string">"ASF云挂卡中 "</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"CustomGamePlayedWhileIdle"</span>: <span class="string">"ASF云挂卡已完成"</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"DismissInventoryNotifications"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"Enabled"</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"FarmingOrder"</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"FarmOffline"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"GamesPlayedWhileIdle"</span>: [</div><div class="line">    <span class="number">206440</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="number">730</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="number">385800</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="number">333600</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="number">420110</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="number">602520</span>  </div><div class="line">  ],</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"HandleOfflineMessages"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"IsBotAccount"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"LootableTypes"</span>: [</div><div class="line">    <span class="number">1</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="number">3</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="number">5</span></div><div class="line">  ],</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"PasswordFormat"</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"Paused"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"RedeemingPreferences"</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"SendOnFarmingFinished"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"SendTradePeriod"</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"ShutdownOnFarmingFinished"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"SteamLogin"</span>: <span class="string">"huangjiamianbao"</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"SteamMasterClanID"</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"SteamParentalPIN"</span>: <span class="string">"0"</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"SteamPassword"</span>: <span class="string">"我的steam密码"</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"SteamTradeToken"</span>: <span class="literal">null</span>,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"SteamUserPermissions"</span>: &#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attr">"76561198384518469"</span>: <span class="number">3</span></div><div class="line">  &#125;,</div><div class="line">  <span class="attr">"TradingPreferences"</span>: <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<hr>
<h1 id="安装mono（以centos6为例）"><a href="#安装mono（以centos6为例）" class="headerlink" title="安装mono（以centos6为例）"></a>安装mono（以centos6为例）</h1><p>ASF在Windows上运行需要.NET，而在centos下则需要mono</p>
<figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">yum install yum-utils</div><div class="line">rpm --<span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="string">"http://keyserver.ubuntu.com/pks/lookup?op=get&amp;search=0x3FA7E0328081BFF6A14DA29AA6A19B38D3D831EF"</span></div><div class="line">yum-<span class="built_in">config</span>-manager --add-repo http:<span class="comment">//download.mono-project.com/repo/centos6/</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><code>yum install mono-complete</code></p>
<p>检查<code>mono -V</code></p>
<p>参见<a href="http://www.mono-project.com/download/" target="_blank" rel="external">Mono</a></p>
<h1 id="上传ASF"><a href="#上传ASF" class="headerlink" title="上传ASF"></a>上传ASF</h1><p>上传ASF.exe和config文件夹到VPS</p>
<h2 id="Windows"><a href="#Windows" class="headerlink" title="Windows"></a>Windows</h2><p>FlashFXP，官网疑似gg，自行下载<br>在站点管理器中填写好信息后上传</p>
<h2 id="android"><a href="#android" class="headerlink" title="android"></a>android</h2><p>Google Play下载AndFTP<br>或在此下载<a href="http://www.apkmirror.com/apk/lysesoft/andftp-your-ftp-client/andftp-your-ftp-client-4-3-release/andftp-ftp-client-4-3-android-apk-download/" target="_blank" rel="external">AndFTP</a></p>
<p>填写好域名，类型，用户名，密码后上传</p>
<p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/26/59282ff9180bb.jpg" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="其他系统"><a href="#其他系统" class="headerlink" title="其他系统"></a>其他系统</h2><p>未知</p>
<h1 id="mono运行ASF"><a href="#mono运行ASF" class="headerlink" title="mono运行ASF"></a>mono运行ASF</h1><p><code>screen -S asf</code><br>后台运行ASF</p>
<p><code>cd ASF</code><br>打开ASF目录</p>
<p><code>mono ASF.exe</code><br>使用mono运行ASF</p>
<p>ASF成功打开后（可能需要输入手机令牌），就可以关闭连接</p>
<h1 id="后期维护"><a href="#后期维护" class="headerlink" title="后期维护"></a>后期维护</h1><p><code>screen -ls</code><br>查看后台</p>
<p><code>kill 进程号</code><br>关闭后台进程</p>
<p><code>screen -r 进程名</code><br>恢复后台进程</p>
<h1 id="ASF高级应用"><a href="#ASF高级应用" class="headerlink" title="ASF高级应用"></a>ASF高级应用</h1><p><del>这是最新的操作</del></p>
<ul>
<li>自定义状态显示 </li>
<li>挂游戏时长</li>
<li>自动批量激活游戏key</li>
<li>等</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/26/592833c628ceb.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/26/592833c639a48.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/26/592833c64f0b8.jpg" alt=""></p>
]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
