    <title>VPS翻墙教程（shadowsocks）</title>
    <link href="https://huangjiaming.com/2017/05/12/vps1/"/>
    <id>https://huangjiaming.com/2017/05/12/vps1/</id>
    <published>2017-05-12T04:33:41.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-06-01T14:26:03.975Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<script src="/assets/js/DPlayer.min.js"> </script><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js"> </script><p>刚搞好博客，有几个大佬想让我写写教程，于是我顺便把博客相关的东西都写写，由于我比较弱，教程尽量采用能省就省，不求甚解的风格，有问题欢迎在评论区提出或私下联系我</p>
<p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/18/591d52a6e9d95.jpeg" alt=""></p>
<iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="330" height="450" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=0&id=157137810&auto=1&height=430"></iframe>

<hr>
<h1 id="理论基础"><a href="#理论基础" class="headerlink" title="理论基础"></a>理论基础</h1><h2 id="VPS"><a href="#VPS" class="headerlink" title="VPS"></a>VPS</h2><blockquote>
<p>虚拟专用伺服器（英语：Virtual private server，缩写为 VPS），是将一台服务器分割成多个虚拟专享服务器的服务。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="墙"><a href="#墙" class="headerlink" title="墙"></a>墙</h2><blockquote>
<p>防火长城（英语：Great Firewall (of China)，常用简称：GFW，中文也称中国国家防火墙，中国大陆民众俗称防火墙等），是对中华人民共和国政府在其互联网边界审查系统（包括相关行政审查系统）的统称。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="翻墙"><a href="#翻墙" class="headerlink" title="翻墙"></a>翻墙</h2><blockquote>
<p>突破网络审查或突破网络封锁，在中国大陆突破防火长城实行的网络审查又叫翻墙或科学上网，指绕过互联网审查封锁技术（IP封锁、端口封锁、关键词过滤、域名劫持等），实现对网络内容的访问。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="shadowsocks"><a href="#shadowsocks" class="headerlink" title="shadowsocks"></a>shadowsocks</h2><blockquote>
<p>shadowsocks是一种基于Socks5代理方式的网路资料加密传输套件，并采用Apache许可证、GPL、MIT许可证等多种自由软体许可协定开放原始码。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="shadowsocks的特点"><a href="#shadowsocks的特点" class="headerlink" title="shadowsocks的特点"></a>shadowsocks的特点</h2><ul>
<li>Shadowsocks使用自行设计的协议进行加密通信。加密算法有AES、Blowfish、IDEA、RC4等，除建立TCP连接外无需握手，每次请求只转发一个连接，因此使用起来网速较快，在移动设备上也比较省电。</li>
<li>所有的流量都经过算法加密，允许自行选择算法，所以比较安全。</li>
<li>Shadowsocks通过异步I/O和事件驱动程序运行，响应速度快。</li>
<li>客户端覆盖多个主流操作系统和平台，包括Windows、OS X、Android和iOS系统和路由器（OpenWrt）等。</li>
<li>专为移动设备和无线网络优化。</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<blockquote>
<p>如果你想使用ss翻墙，但懒于DIY，欢迎<a href="http://huangjiaming.com/about/">联系我与我合租VPS</a></p>
<p>如果你想免费翻墙，请参阅GAE，VPN，DNS/hosts法，免费ss等</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h1 id="实际操作"><a href="#实际操作" class="headerlink" title="实际操作"></a>实际操作</h1><h2 id="客户端-下载"><a href="#客户端-下载" class="headerlink" title="客户端 下载"></a>客户端 下载</h2><h3 id="Windows"><a href="#Windows" class="headerlink" title="Windows"></a>Windows</h3><p>参见<br><a href="https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks-windows/wiki/Shadowsocks-Windows-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E" target="_blank" rel="external">github</a></p>
<h3 id="macOS"><a href="#macOS" class="headerlink" title="macOS"></a>macOS</h3><p>参见<br><a href="https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks-iOS/wiki/Shadowsocks-for-OSX-%E5%B8%AE%E5%8A%A9" target="_blank" rel="external">github</a></p>
<h3 id="iOS"><a href="#iOS" class="headerlink" title="iOS"></a>iOS</h3><p>App Store中</p>
<p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/18/591d52a7f0ba9.png" alt=""><br><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/18/591d52a828bc2.png" alt=""><br><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/18/591d52a88e0e8.png" alt=""></p>
<p>个人推荐take（也是我现在用的）（自带免费ss）<br>iOS似乎目前还没有免费的ss客户端</p>
<h3 id="android"><a href="#android" class="headerlink" title="android"></a>android</h3><p>Google Play下载Shadowsocks<br>或在此下载<a href="http://www.apkmirror.com/apk/max-lv/shadowsocks/shadowsocks-4-1-7-release/shadowsocks-4-1-7-android-apk-download/" target="_blank" rel="external">Shadowsocks</a></p>
<h2 id="VPS-购买"><a href="#VPS-购买" class="headerlink" title="VPS 购买"></a>VPS 购买</h2><p>你需要一台海外（墙外）的vps<br>这里我推荐的（现在用的）是vultr的日本东京机房，当然你要说我做广告我也没办法(╯°□°）╯︵ ┻━┻<br><a href="vultr.com">vultr</a><br><a href="http://www.vultr.com/?ref=7151882" target="_blank" rel="external">如果用这个链接注册我似乎能拿到钱？</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p>其他vps推荐参考<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/20800554" target="_blank" rel="external">逼乎</a></p>
</blockquote>
<p>VPS规格挑选（以vultr为例）</p>
<ol>
<li>类型选择Vultr Cloud Compute(VC2)</li>
<li>地点建议选择日本东京（低ping）</li>
<li>系统选择64 bit OS中的Centos 6 x64</li>
<li>配置选择最低配就行<blockquote>
<p>$5/月（按小时计费）<br>25G SSD<br>1 CPU<br>1G 内存<br>1000G 流量</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li>下面的选项不用更改，点击<strong>Deploy Now</strong><br>稍等一会，VPS就会安装好系统，并且你会收到一封邮件<br>在vultr中找到你的VPS，你需要记下三个信息</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>IP</li>
<li>用户名</li>
<li>密码</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/18/591d52a817e2e.jpeg" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="VPS-连接"><a href="#VPS-连接" class="headerlink" title="VPS 连接"></a>VPS 连接</h2><h3 id="Windows-1"><a href="#Windows-1" class="headerlink" title="Windows"></a>Windows</h3><p><a href="http://www.putty.org/" target="_blank" rel="external">putty</a><br>安装后打开，输入IP，点击连接，弹出黑色的连接页<br>先输入用户名，回车后输入密码</p>
<blockquote>
<p>密码输入时没有任何显示，输入完后回车即可</p>
<p>粘贴是右键，不是Ctrl+V</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="macOS-1"><a href="#macOS-1" class="headerlink" title="macOS"></a>macOS</h3><p>参见<br><a href="https://www.quora.com/What-is-the-equivalent-of-PuTTY-for-Mac-OS-X" target="_blank" rel="external">Quora</a><br>和Windows部分</p>
<h3 id="iOS-1"><a href="#iOS-1" class="headerlink" title="iOS"></a>iOS</h3><p>App Store下载Termius<br>在Hosts中点击加号，选择New Hosts，如图填写</p>
<p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/18/591d52a820289.jpeg" alt=""></p>
<h3 id="android-1"><a href="#android-1" class="headerlink" title="android"></a>android</h3><p>Google Play下载ConnectBot<br>或在此下载<a href="http://www.apkmirror.com/apk/kenny-root-jeff-sharkey-torne-wuff-paul-evans/connectbot/connectbot-1-9-2-release/connectbot-1-9-2-android-apk-download/" target="_blank" rel="external">ConnectBot</a><br>点击加号，如图填写（IP，用户名，开始Shell会话）</p>
<p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/26/5927c5a319f56.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/26/5927c5d9d7c3e.jpg" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="VPS-shadowsocks的安装"><a href="#VPS-shadowsocks的安装" class="headerlink" title="VPS shadowsocks的安装"></a>VPS shadowsocks的安装</h2><p>输入<br><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">wget --<span class="keyword">no</span>-check-certificate -O shadowsocks-libev.<span class="keyword">sh</span> http<span class="variable">s:</span>//raw.githubusercontent.<span class="keyword">com</span>/teddysun/shadowsocks_install/master/shadowsocks-libev.<span class="keyword">sh</span></div><div class="line">chmod +<span class="keyword">x</span> shadowsocks-libev.<span class="keyword">sh</span></div><div class="line">./shadowsocks-libev.<span class="keyword">sh</span> <span class="number">2</span>&gt;&amp;<span class="number">1</span> | tee shadowsocks-libev.<span class="built_in">log</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>后填写信息 一路回车</p>
<ul>
<li>port 默认即可或自己设个端口</li>
<li>password 自己设个密码<br>耐心等待 等到看到<figure class="highlight oxygene"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">Congratulations, Shadowsocks-libev install completed!</div><div class="line">Your Server IP:your_server_ip</div><div class="line">Your Server Port:your_server_port</div><div class="line">Your Password:your_password</div><div class="line">Your Local IP:<span class="number">127.0</span>.<span class="number">0.1</span></div><div class="line">Your Local Port:<span class="number">1080</span></div><div class="line">Your Encryption <span class="function"><span class="keyword">Method</span>:</span>aes-<span class="number">256</span>-cfb</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">Welcome <span class="keyword">to</span> visit:https:<span class="comment">//teddysun.com/357.html</span></div><div class="line">Enjoy it!</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<p>的时候，安装完成<br>参见：<a href="https://teddysun.com/357.html" target="_blank" rel="external">一键安装脚本说明</a></p>
<h2 id="VPS-安装锐速破解版提速"><a href="#VPS-安装锐速破解版提速" class="headerlink" title="VPS 安装锐速破解版提速"></a>VPS 安装锐速破解版提速</h2><p>分别输入<br><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">rpm -ivh http:<span class="regexp">//</span>soft.<span class="number">91</span>yun.org<span class="regexp">/ISO/</span>Linux<span class="regexp">/CentOS/</span>kernel<span class="regexp">/kernel-firmware-2.6.32-504.3.3.el6.noarch.rpm</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>和<br><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">rpm -ivh http:<span class="regexp">//</span>soft.<span class="number">91</span>yun.org<span class="regexp">/ISO/</span>Linux<span class="regexp">/CentOS/</span>kernel<span class="regexp">/kernel-2.6.32-504.3.3.el6.x86_64.rpm --force</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>来更换内核</p>
<p>安装完后重启<code>reboot</code><br>检查是否更换完成<code>uname -r</code><br>如果显示为<br><code>kernel-2.6.32-504.3.3.el6.x86_64</code><br>说明一切正常<br>之后输入<br><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">wget -<span class="keyword">N</span> --<span class="keyword">no</span>-check-certificate http<span class="variable">s:</span>//github.<span class="keyword">com</span>/<span class="number">91</span>yun/serverspeeder/raw/master/serverspeeder.<span class="keyword">sh</span> &amp;&amp; bash serverspeeder.<span class="keyword">sh</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>来一键安装锐速破解版<br>至此，VPS完成<br>参见：<a href="https://github.com/91yun/serverspeeder/blob/master/README.md" target="_blank" rel="external">GitHub</a></p>
<h2 id="客户端-配置"><a href="#客户端-配置" class="headerlink" title="客户端 配置"></a>客户端 配置</h2><p>以iOS take和android shadowsocks为例，其他客户端大同小异，配置好即可开始使用</p>
<h3 id="iOS-take"><a href="#iOS-take" class="headerlink" title="iOS take"></a>iOS take</h3><p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/18/591d54e7d7c07.jpeg" alt=""></p>
<h3 id="android-shadowsocks"><a href="#android-shadowsocks" class="headerlink" title="android shadowsocks"></a>android shadowsocks</h3><p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/26/5927ea7ba1088.jpg" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="VPS-shadowsocks后期维护"><a href="#VPS-shadowsocks后期维护" class="headerlink" title="VPS shadowsocks后期维护"></a>VPS shadowsocks后期维护</h2><p>启动 <code>/etc/init.d/shadowsocks start</code><br>停止 <code>/etc/init.d/shadowsocks stop</code><br>重启 <code>/etc/init.d/shadowsocks restart</code><br>查看状态 <code>/etc/init.d/shadowsocks status</code></p>
]]></content>
    
